commit_message: Make sure concept labels are of a read-only Mapping type

Add some properties to Taxonomy object for finding the languages supported (supportedLanguages) by the concept & group labels of the taxonomy, the most commonly used language in the taxonomy (defaultLanguage, one with most labels) and helper (getBestSupportedLanguage) to find the best taxonomy language to use, making use of localise.getBestSupportedLanguage()

commit_message: Add some properties to Taxonomy object for finding the languages supported (supportedLanguages) by the concept & group labels of the taxonomy, the most commonly used language in the taxonomy (defaultLanguage, one with most labels) and helper (getBestSupportedLanguage) to find the best taxonomy language to use, making use of localise.getBestSupportedLanguage()
Change API for PresentationGroup so you can now get the label for a language rather than only supporting the English labels
